<h2>
    Salmon Fishing Regulations and Tags in Oregon
</h2>
<p>
    Oregon fishing law requires:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Oregon Angling License</strong> (ages 12+)
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Combined Angling Tag</strong> for salmon/steelhead
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Adipose fin requirement</strong>: Only hatchery fish with clipped fins may be kept unless otherwise specified.
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
